The paper deals with online convex optimization, which is a subfield of machine learning and optimization. The algorithm proposed in the paper, MetaGrad, is a parameter-free algorithm that automatically tunes the learning rate parameter for the data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
